---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout
  titleSv="Vår process — Sigvardsson Consulting Group"
  titleEn="Our Process — Sigvardsson Consulting Group"
  descriptionSv="30+ år av processutveckling inom retail. Vår beprövade 5-stegsprocess levererar mätbar ROI i varje projekt."
  descriptionEn="30+ years of process development in retail. Our proven 5-step process delivers measurable ROI in every project."
  canonical="https://www.sigvardsson.org/our-process/"
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label sv-text">Vår process</span>
      <span class="section-label en-text">Our process</span>
      <h1>
        <span class="sv-text">Beprövad process.<br/>Mätbara resultat.</span>
        <span class="en-text">Proven process.<br/>Measurable results.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub sv-text">En strukturerad 5-stegsprocess byggd på 30+ år av retailerfarenhet och 250+ genomförda projekt.</p>
      <p class="hero-sub en-text">A structured 5-step process built on 30+ years of retail experience and 250+ completed projects.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process-steps-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="steps-list">
        <div class="step-row fade-up">
          <div class="step-num">01</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h2><span class="sv-text">Analys & kartläggning</span><span class="en-text">Analysis & mapping</span></h2>
            <p><span class="sv-text">Vi analyserar din verksamhet på djupet — data, processer, organisation och marknad. Vi identifierar var den verkliga förbättringspotentialen finns och prioriterar åtgärder med högst ROI.</span><span class="en-text">We deeply analyze your business — data, processes, organization and market. We identify where the real improvement potential lies and prioritize actions with the highest ROI.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row fade-up" style="animation-delay:80ms">
          <div class="step-num">02</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h2><span class="sv-text">Strategi & plan</span><span class="en-text">Strategy & plan</span></h2>
            <p><span class="sv-text">Baserat på analysen tar vi fram en konkret strategi med tydliga mål, ansvar och tidplan. Vi definierar vilka av våra verktyg och metoder som passar bäst för din specifika situation.</span><span class="en-text">Based on the analysis, we develop a concrete strategy with clear goals, accountability and timeline. We define which of our tools and methods best fit your specific situation.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row fade-up" style="animation-delay:160ms">
          <div class="step-num">03</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h2><span class="sv-text">Implementering</span><span class="en-text">Implementation</span></h2>
            <p><span class="sv-text">Hands-on genomförande av projektet med ditt team. Mobil-first, datadrivet och med fokus på omedelbar effekt. Vi är med i butiken, inte bara i mötesrummet.</span><span class="en-text">Hands-on project execution with your team. Mobile-first, data-driven and focused on immediate impact. We are in the store, not just in the meeting room.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row fade-up" style="animation-delay:240ms">
          <div class="step-num">04</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h2><span class="sv-text">Mät & justera</span><span class="en-text">Measure & adjust</span></h2>
            <p><span class="sv-text">Kontinuerlig mätning av resultat mot uppsatta mål. Vi justerar löpande baserat på data och insikter för att maximera effekten. Transparens och evidensbaserat beslutsfattande.</span><span class="en-text">Continuous measurement of results against set targets. We continuously adjust based on data and insights to maximize impact. Transparency and evidence-based decision making.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row fade-up" style="animation-delay:320ms">
          <div class="step-num">05</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h2><span class="sv-text">Skala upp & befäst</span><span class="en-text">Scale up & consolidate</span></h2>
            <p><span class="sv-text">När resultaten är bevisade skalar vi upp till fler butiker och kategorier. Vi bygger intern kompetens, dokumenterar processer och säkerställer att förändringen håller långsiktigt.</span><span class="en-text">When results are proven, we scale up to more stores and categories. We build internal competence, document processes and ensure the change lasts long-term.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="principles">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="fade-up"><span class="sv-text">Våra principer</span><span class="en-text">Our principles</span></h2>
      <div class="principles-grid">
        <div class="principle fade-up">
          <h3><span class="sv-text">Omedelbar ROI</span><span class="en-text">Immediate ROI</span></h3>
          <p><span class="sv-text">Varje projekt levererar mätbar avkastning från dag ett.</span><span class="en-text">Every project delivers measurable return from day one.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle fade-up" style="animation-delay:80ms">
          <h3><span class="sv-text">Mobil-first</span><span class="en-text">Mobile-first</span></h3>
          <p><span class="sv-text">Alla verktyg är byggda för butikspersonal i rörelse.</span><span class="en-text">All tools are built for store staff on the move.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle fade-up" style="animation-delay:160ms">
          <h3><span class="sv-text">Datadriven</span><span class="en-text">Data-driven</span></h3>
          <p><span class="sv-text">Beslut baseras på fakta, inte intuition.</span><span class="en-text">Decisions are based on facts, not intuition.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle fade-up" style="animation-delay:240ms">
          <h3><span class="sv-text">Långsiktighet</span><span class="en-text">Long-term thinking</span></h3>
          <p><span class="sv-text">Vi bygger relationer och kompetens som håller.</span><span class="en-text">We build relationships and competence that lasts.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center">
      <h2 class="fade-up">
        <span class="sv-text">Redo att sätta igång?</span>
        <span class="en-text">Ready to get started?</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="cta-row fade-up">
        <a href="/Contact/" class="btn btn-light sv-text">Kontakta oss</a>
        <a href="/Contact/" class="btn btn-light en-text">Contact us</a>
        <a href="/services/" class="btn btn-outline sv-text">Se tjänster →</a>
        <a href="/services/" class="btn btn-outline en-text">See services →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>

<style>
.page-hero { background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--color-navy) 0%,var(--color-blue) 100%);color:var(--color-white);padding:5rem 2rem 4rem; }
.page-hero .section-label { color:var(--color-blue-lite); }
.page-hero h1 { font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.5rem);line-height:1.1;margin:.75rem 0 1.25rem; }
.hero-sub { font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);max-width:600px;line-height:1.7; }
.process-steps-section { padding:5rem 2rem; }
.steps-list { display:flex;flex-direction:column; }
.step-row { display:grid;grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;gap:2.5rem;padding:2.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(1,13,96,.08); }
.step-row:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.step-num { font-family:'Chakra Petch',sans-serif;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-blue-lite);line-height:1; }
.step-content h2 { font-size:1.4rem;color:var(--color-navy);margin-bottom:.75rem; }
.step-content p { color:rgba(1,13,96,.7);line-height:1.75;max-width:640px; }
.principles { background:var(--color-off-white);padding:5rem 2rem; }
.principles h2 { font-size:1.75rem;color:var(--color-navy);margin-bottom:2.5rem; }
.principles-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1.5rem; }
.principle { background:var(--color-white);border-radius:12px;padding:1.75rem;border:1px solid rgba(1,13,96,.08); }
.principle h3 { font-size:1rem;color:var(--color-navy);margin-bottom:.6rem; }
.principle p { font-size:.875rem;color:rgba(1,13,96,.65);line-height:1.65; }
.cta-band { background:var(--color-navy);padding:4.5rem 2rem;color:var(--color-white); }
.cta-band h2 { font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem);margin-bottom:2rem; }
.cta-row { display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap; }
.btn-light { background:var(--color-white);color:var(--color-navy);font-family:'Chakra Petch',sans-serif;font-weight:500;padding:.75rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:.95rem;transition:all .2s;display:inline-block; }
.btn-light:hover { background:var(--color-off-white);transform:translateY(-2px); }
.btn-outline { background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);font-family:'Chakra Petch',sans-serif;font-weight:500;padding:.75rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:.95rem;transition:all .2s;display:inline-block; }
.btn-outline:hover { border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);color:var(--color-white); }
@media(max-width:900px){ .principles-grid { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); } }
@media(max-width:600px){ .step-row { grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1rem; }.principles-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
</style>
